   Find your piece of paradise in our luxury Boutique Hotel Matlai in
   Michamwi, on the south-east coast of the fair and beautiful island of
   Zanzibar, East Africa. You will find a unique and extraordinary beach
   accommodation embedded in an amazing tropical garden overlooking the
   turquoise Indian Ocean. Boutique Hotel Matlai is designed as an
   exclusive villa resort for people seeking a high level of comfort and
   privacy in a relaxed atmosphere. Spoil yourself under tropical palm
   trees and enjoy peace and quiet away from the hustle and bustle of
   modern life ...

